name: Garfield - Caught in the Act [SG]
description:
Garfield: Caught in the Act is an arcade-platformer game developed by SEGA, Point of View and Novotrade International. It was originally released in 1995. It was published by SEGA. The game is rated as "Meh" on RAWG.
Garfield: Caught in the Act is available on Game Gear, PC and Genesis.
